    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It is the classic freeze issue in a much broader way.\r\n\r\nWhen an aircraft tries to attack a frozen actor through `Attack.TickAttack`, it'll sequence a `HeliFly` before the attack activity with the unit's sight ranges at https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/863091d5ccbc218ea3aa4e8fc2d6dcc06e3e0ad5/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Attack.cs#L107.\r\n\r\nHowever, there's an edge case in which the queued `HeliFly` would return immediately at https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/863091d5ccbc218ea3aa4e8fc2d6dcc06e3e0ad5/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Air/HeliFly.cs#L91-L93\r\n\r\nand the game ends up within `Attack.TickAttack` imminently.\r\n\r\nI have `RevealShroud->Type: GroundPosition` on my aircraft and I feel that's a contributing factor here but these are definitely steps of the freeze."
  },
