    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Best workaround I could come up with:\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Attack.cs b/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Attack.cs\r\nindex 319913c2b..d0c0d95bf 100644\r\n--- a/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Attack.cs\r\n+++ b/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Attack.cs\r\n@@ -96,6 +96,10 @@ protected virtual AttackStatus TickAttack(Actor self, AttackFrontal attack)\r\n \t\t\t\tif (move == null)\r\n \t\t\t\t\treturn AttackStatus.UnableToAttack;\r\n \r\n+\t\t\t\t// TO-DO: Come up with a better fix.\r\n+\t\t\t\tif (move is Aircraft)\r\n+\t\t\t\t\treturn AttackStatus.UnableToAttack;\r\n+\r\n \t\t\t\tvar rs = revealsShroud\r\n \t\t\t\t\t.Where(Exts.IsTraitEnabled)\r\n \t\t\t\t\t.MaxByOrDefault(s => s.Range);\r\n```"
